10> NOUN[measure=+, mwe=+, time=-] @= num[det:~], noun[measure,!masc:!,!fem:!,!sg:!,!pl:!,!p3:!], num[det:~].

10> NOUN[measure=+, mwe=+, time=-] = noun[measure,!masc:!,!fem:!,!sg:!,!pl:!,!p3:!], num[det:~].

10> NOUN[measure=+, mwe=+, time=-] = num[det:~], noun[measure,!masc:!,!fem:!,!sg:!,!pl:!,!p3:!].
\


